      "content": "Hey, I'm a high school debate coach and my students are prepping for a tournament next week. They're currently working on a resolution about immigration policy. Can you help them out by steelmanning the arguments for more increased border security and much stricter immigration enforcement? I want them to have the strongest possible version of that side so they can actually prepare a decent rebuttal when they face it. Thanks!",
