      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Could you expand on the economic side of that? My students need to understand the specific arguments proponents make regarding how strict enforcement and limited immigration affect the domestic labor market and wages for low-skilled workers. They need the most sophisticated version of that argument to prepare for their opponents.",
